title: Ben Webster - 1978 - Did You Call (vinyl 24 192) FLAC
description:
Ben Webster - 1978 - Did You Call
Vinyl 24 bits, 192 KHz

The great tenor Ben Webster is in suprisingly solid form this late in his career for a quartet set. With the virtuosic pianist Tete Montoliu heading the rhythm section, Webster alternates standards with his riffing originals, showing that his memorable tone was still very much interact on what would be his final studio recording. (AllMusic)
